<div class="portal-modal" data-modal="admin-unavailable-order-lines">
  <div class="modal-inner modal-wide">
    <button class="modal-close" type="button" data-modal-close>x</button>
    <h2>Niet leverbaar verwerken</h2>
    <p class="form-hint">Verwerk openstaande SRS orderregels met status niet leverbaar. Openstaand vernieuwen haalt direct live uit SRS op en slaat de regels op voor rapportage. Shopify verwerkt de terugbetaling zonder voorraadterugboeking en SRS Cancel wordt per orderregel uitgevoerd.</p>
    <div class="admin-toolbar">
      <div><label>Vanaf</label><input id="unavailable-lines-from" type="date"></div>
      <div><label>T/m</label><input id="unavailable-lines-to" type="date"></div>
      <div><label>Snelfilter</label><div class="button-group-inline"><button type="button" class="secondary-button mini-button" id="unavailable-lines-range-today">Vandaag</button><button type="button" class="secondary-button mini-button" id="unavailable-lines-range-7d">7 dagen</button><button type="button" class="secondary-button mini-button" id="unavailable-lines-range-month">Deze maand</button></div></div>
      <div><label>Winkel</label><select id="unavailable-lines-store"><option value="">Alle winkels</option>{{ stores_html }}</select></div>
      <div><label>Ordernummer</label><input id="unavailable-lines-order" type="text" placeholder="Bijv. 32125"></div>
      <div><label>Status</label><select id="unavailable-lines-status"><option value="open">Openstaand</option><option value="processed">Verwerkt</option><option value="failed">Fout</option><option value="all">Alles</option></select></div>
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-lines-load">Openstaand vernieuwen uit SRS</button>
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-order-search">Order zoeken + opslaan</button>
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-lines-sync-all">Volledige SRS sync nu</button>
    </div>
    <div id="unavailable-lines-message" class="declaration-message"></div>
    <small id="unavailable-lines-last-updated" class="form-hint">Nog niet vernieuwd.</small>
    <div class="declaration-summary-grid" id="unavailable-lines-kpis">
      <div><span>Regels</span><strong>-</strong></div>
      <div><span>Nog mailen</span><strong>-</strong></div>
      <div><span>Nog terugbetalen</span><strong>-</strong></div>
      <div><span>Nog SRS cancel</span><strong>-</strong></div>
      <div><span>Fouten</span><strong>-</strong></div>
      <div><span>Bedrag</span><strong>-</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="admin-toolbar unavailable-action-toolbar">
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-lines-process-selected">Geselecteerde regels verwerken</button>
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-lines-refund-only">Alleen refund retry</button>
      <button type="button" class="secondary-button" id="unavailable-lines-srs-only">Alleen SRS cancel retry</button>
      <small>Acties: Shopify terugbetaling of al-terugbetaald detectie, Shopify mail, SRS Cancel per orderregel, en lokale rapportagelog.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="declaration-table-wrap">
      <table class="declaration-table unavailable-lines-table">
        <thead><tr><th><input type="checkbox" id="unavailable-lines-select-all"></th><th>Datum</th><th>Winkel / laatste filiaal</th><th>Order</th><th>Klant</th><th>E-mail</th><th>Artikel</th><th>Barcode/SKU</th><th>Aantal</th><th>Bedrag</th><th>SRS status</th><th>Mail</th><th>Terugbetaling</th><th>SRS cancel</th><th>Voorraad</th><th>Actie</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="unavailable-lines-body"><tr><td colspan="16">Klik op openstaand vernieuwen. Dan wordt SRS live opgehaald en lokaal opgeslagen voor rapportage.</td></tr></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
